&gt;Droidcon SF 2022&lt;/a&gt;, first conference outside of South Africa after the lockdown years. I was so happy to be part of the speakers for my talk titled &lt;code&gt;Something old, something new - adding Jetpack Compose to a large open source app&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
